				    	BeatTree relies heavily on Spotify to allow you to play music directly from the browser.  We use Spotify because we think it's a great product.  If you already have the Spotify client, open it up and you're good to go.  If you're not a Spotify user, click the Spotify icon to the left to get a free one-month trial of their Premium service.
