				    <h4 class="media-heading">Use a Computer</h4>
				    <p>
				    	BeatTree will run on most mobile devices, but integration with Spotify is not as seamless.  Additionally, viewing any part of the website which includes elements from the D3.js library (graph views) will be very slow.  For best results, use a desktop or laptop.
